{"tid":146291,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"目前nintendo switch的災情如下","createTime":"2017-03-07T03:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T15:46:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":16,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb37c8bc5468e17f6c5ff07581cf93ff018f303","tid":146291,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:27:45.000Z","msg":"目前nintendo switch的災情如下<br />\n<br />\n1 遊戲執行中畫面異常(雪花、雜點、顏色反轉、閃爍)：顯卡問題<br />\n<br />\n2 螢幕出現條狀異常、壞亮點：LCD問題<br />\n<br />\n3 持續不止的雜音：音訊晶片或speaker問題<br />\n<br />\n4 當機(黃藍屏)、按鍵或觸控無反應、畫面凍結：系統穩定性<br />\n<br />\n5 手把延遲或斷訊：藍芽晶片功率問題<br />\n<br />\n6 卡夾插入沒反應：卡夾良率<br />\n<br />\n7 接上dock時螢幕刮傷：機構設計不良<br />\n<br />\n8 手把握套無法拆裝、卡死：零件公差過大<br />\n<br />\n9 掌機模式時手把與主機無法緊密結合，會搖：零件公差過大<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60001&amp;snA=40243&amp;tnum=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60001%26snA%3D40243%26tnum%3D4&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=036a8e84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60001&amp;snA=40243&amp;tnum=4</a>"},{"pid":"8e72ad3605cc770d74f75eed1e245319fcb49143","tid":146291,"uid":12362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"對佢地黎講買唔到機先係最大災情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e1600b4ebe28a487873eec9025ddc1fc58ffcc","tid":146291,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e101af7599e13957913928997f24af893063e84","tid":146291,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n都唔係用Windows點會藍畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/115350_3ef4cffe0be1c875cd090f82028dfda0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F115350_3ef4cffe0be1c875cd090f82028dfda0.jpg&h=b2f276e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用淨色圖當hand機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次試下更蠢D搵部Mac機放張藍色圖話藍畫面啦<br />\n或者An機放張白蘋果圖<br />\n<br />\n樓主你雖然近年叻左<br />\n開好多新聞post攝落出post紀錄度扮唔係打手<br />\n但你D打手post都一如以往常用假新聞扮到真咁<br />\n換湯不換藥<br />\n<br />\n有時間做呢D野不如自己爭氣D搵多D錢啦"},{"pid":"4cb9ce85337f057ff7dedf7c9d72e86f20ad686a","tid":146291,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"暫時見真實問題係<br />\n<br />\n減號掣個位置好難襟<br />\n同埋LR有4粒掣唔夠大粒<br />\n<br />\n打手對真實既問題完全提唔出<br />\n都唔知有冇玩過部機<br />\n但作出一大堆冇乜人講既問題<br />\n<br />\n其實打手幾時先可以進步？<br />\n係咪窮撚學生哥做打手<br />\n窮到連二千幾蚊買部機既錢都慳番<br />\n知己知彼百戰百勝<br />\n你當老任係假想敵<br />\n都要比錢買人地產品用下先可寫文鬧佢得精彩D<br />\n完全零體驗憑空創作又係科技白痴<br />\n放張藍色圖橙色圖就係hang機<br />\n真係假到無朋友<br />\n<br />\nP.S.<br />\n淨色圖通常係用黎試新機mon有冇死點光點時用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWindows藍畫面都係有字架<br />\nSwitch都唔會用Windows囉"},{"pid":"83c3e2cd11b48edc7ed97d8d250fe3dea4f6a60d","tid":146291,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:11:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線<br />\n都唔係用Windows點會藍畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/115350_3ef4cffe0be1c875cd090f82028dfda0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F115350_3ef4cffe0be1c875cd090f82028dfda0.jpg&h=b2f276e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用淨色圖當hand機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次試下更蠢D搵部Mac機放張藍色圖話藍畫面啦<br />\n或者An機放張白蘋果圖<br />\n<br />\n樓主你雖然近年叻左<br />\n開好多新聞post攝落出post紀錄度扮唔係打手<br />\n但你D打手post都一如以往常用假新聞扮到真咁<br />\n換湯不換藥<br />\n<br />\n有時間做呢D野不如自己爭氣D搵多D錢啦</blockquote><br />\n恥笑開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6785f5bd1432d48198783c008b7434c640ece5be","tid":146291,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cb-srOfRqNc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCb-srOfRqNc&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=65650b3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Cb-srOfRqNc</a>"},{"pid":"cbcda858b2dc3b4419b4bbb2e960c692452d589f","tid":146291,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cb-srOfRqNc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCb-srOfRqNc&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=65650b3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Cb-srOfRqNc</a></blockquote><br />\n片都有啦，仲有假？"},{"pid":"96fa0ad6a7c6426e8a56447818a0b21286790bd8","tid":146291,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283824ce40b585670d24cf4f2a1d68c96c68ca1a","tid":146291,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cb-srOfRqNc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCb-srOfRqNc&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=65650b3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Cb-srOfRqNc</a></blockquote><br />\n片都有啦，仲有假？</blockquote><br />\n咁多年黎又唔見你貼下PS遊戲機首發時問題既相或片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪Youtube有但你選擇性搵唔到？<br />\n貼PS機問題片你會唔會減人工架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得閒係連登問下D玩緊Switch既玩家<br />\n有幾多個有呢D災情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好心唔好直接帶高登個套打手玩法黎連登<br />\n過檔連登堆人通常都係較醒又係上網有資深經驗既人<br />\n當中好多都係電腦人<br />\n<br />\n或者你不如改個名扮第二個啦<br />\n分身都唔識扮懶到你呀"},{"pid":"46f4d774bfacb643160f450f39f84ba1e6f28408","tid":146291,"uid":60746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪機主先"},{"pid":"2637174a5453f14bc63bfcb44991a6653aeef077","tid":146291,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76022G0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76022G0.jpg&h=0b2ec331&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLiE69H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLiE69H.jpg&h=5a61e98f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle圖片搵Switch藍畫面<br />\n搵極都係個source係同一張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全球得一個source叫災難咁過癮？<br />\n<br />\n咁我咳一聲<br />\n咪有全球肺炎災難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63249c834f0fa1503288212cac235366bff2e75","tid":146291,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:30:51.000Z","msg":"其實係咪2個打手係到嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9523037e7b6510a15d1243674c7e36a9d0d0e1","tid":146291,"uid":28858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，電子野會輕機有幾咁奇？<br />\n咁都有打手話人地係整張假圖出黎<br />\n如果搵到部機真係好似上面果兩個咁樣輕你係咪成部食撚左佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da03fb3b3f1d2cada8038fe779988338837bbfca","tid":146291,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線，電子野會輕機有幾咁奇？<br />\n咁都有打手話人地係整張假圖出黎<br />\n如果搵到部機真係好似上面果兩個咁樣輕你係咪成部食撚左佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n藍畫面Google圖片得同一張圖"},{"pid":"1a7241550ead687956181c8831146d24b888272b","tid":146291,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"joy con 真係一唔小心就會掉轉左插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n段片拆到爆缸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3312d08d1d64b85c6752bcf49960d8883f3ba9","tid":146291,"uid":19365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>joy con 真係一唔小心就會掉轉左插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n段片拆到爆缸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n官方有片一秒搞掂<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bMMIYWpROsw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbMMIYWpROsw&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=91a2db09\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bMMIYWpROsw</a>"},{"pid":"f60998faf7a24f23afd2407911ef9cc03bf67062","tid":146291,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"無聊，我覺得單新聞得意先share咋，我先無咁得閒嘈交，你要話呢啲係假相咪有得你話囉，我先無咁得閒嘈呢啲無聊野"},{"pid":"15b811694d1acb54eddae48fa483c2d4637acd5e","tid":146291,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪2個打手係到嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係我連登出post紀錄<br />\n高登已無上好耐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/123727_d3d7ffb23e7e77a152cc4af81371caa9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F123727_d3d7ffb23e7e77a152cc4af81371caa9.jpg&h=4d73805d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/123728_7c10ac71d83f94dd99222220b95f19bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F123728_7c10ac71d83f94dd99222220b95f19bb.jpg&h=aac71d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主最近至少出左8個插老任既post<br />\n當中絕大部份都係直接插Switch<br />\n但佢不斷轉貼新聞post攝入其中等你唔太覺係打手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/124047_ed50565249e48bc1c3630b63f81b8841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F124047_ed50565249e48bc1c3630b63f81b8841.jpg&h=e0d4e61f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/124048_1aec49996b085ad8d1c929eded77eb79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F124048_1aec49996b085ad8d1c929eded77eb79.jpg&h=a0b983ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hF2Q14g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhF2Q14g.jpg&h=98b210b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/124049_b3972953ee20f79193e8110da58e4243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F124049_b3972953ee20f79193e8110da58e4243.jpg&h=760885df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F25v52t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF25v52t.jpg&h=b7fab71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8k87B8Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8k87B8Q.jpg&h=a155d3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果資深高登會員都分唔到打手係咩行為<br />\n咁你都幾弱智<br />\n我玩左高登十幾年<br />\n依家改玩連登<br />\n眼見高登D低質打手直接搬高登個套打手玩法黎連登<br />\n依家衰到連尼住都不斷比人開新post惡意中傷<br />\n最咁搞落去連登真係越黎越似高登"},{"pid":"4f9aa7f8bb52a0e876384a5abc653fc17306d20d","tid":146291,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:46:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無聊，我覺得單新聞得意先share咋，我先無咁得閒嘈交，你要話呢啲係假相咪有得你話囉，我先無咁得閒嘈呢啲無聊野</blockquote><br />\n但你最近有8個新post插老任/Switch<br />\n<br />\n完全唔知為乜<br />\n好似其他遊戲機或遊戲公司無新聞夠得意比你轉貼咁"},{"pid":"01783d711251842b329d2bb95928a559f35ecfce","tid":146291,"uid":24512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:53:21.000Z","msg":"玩左5日 暫時都無上述問題"},{"pid":"0a5d3bbe941336cc7dcfd000c3836e7deddfbfa0","tid":146291,"uid":438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:58:04.000Z","msg":"嘈左咁多年<br />\n你兩個有冇諗住結婚"},{"pid":"fdb685a37cc7d77257f0c56eb598a8f7e202fb2c","tid":146291,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"我係樓主你<br />\n就自動等個post沉底啦<br />\n費事我上面貼你點做打手既証據比太多人睇到啦<br />\n<br />\n教精你啦<br />\n開十幾個轉貼新聞post攝落插老任post之間係唔夠架<br />\n應該攝一千幾百個新聞post我先唔會發現你打向既痕跡<br />\n<br />\n我都無心同你嘈架<br />\n我只係唔慣見D打手N年都食老本同一屎橋用N次咁悶<br />\n<br />\n你下次比多D心意同誠意<br />\n親自買部已壞左既Switch<br />\n貼埋身份證上黎話自用<br />\n我覺得你夠可憐就唔會想入黎恥笑你"},{"pid":"72c01dd655ede1fb6b2095b01eb529d4758456a5","tid":146291,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘈左咁多年<br />\n你兩個有冇諗住結婚</blockquote><br />\ngay post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c999a80f38892e473a14072e5063f629cd94bc","tid":146291,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘈左咁多年<br />\n你兩個有冇諗住結婚</blockquote><br />\n其實係源自S字頭公司既marketing唔肯收手插對手<br />\n<br />\n無機界原種不停出同類post<br />\n我邊度有位入黎講佢呀<br />\n<br />\n每次有非PS既新遊戲機出<br />\n就有人不停開工出新post啦<br />\n好似個定律咁<br />\n我都係順住佢個定律又發現人地又開工"},{"pid":"8a991312e430cffd3b6bbbd26a1ef6c45a7ecaaa","tid":146291,"uid":6124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:05:00.000Z","msg":"乜尻災情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f7feb4765608f2d1b8197269ca2da714edd6e0","tid":146291,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘈左咁多年<br />\n你兩個有冇諗住結婚</blockquote><br />\ngay post<img src=\"/assets/