 />\n如果搵到部機真係好似上面果兩個咁樣輕你係咪成部食撚左佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n藍畫面Google圖片得同一張圖</blockquote><br />\n又話係假圖既 宜家又唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無限搬龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceaddf81530b6476a92db6582590330601b2c5b","tid":146291,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線<br />\n都唔係用Windows點會藍畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/115350_3ef4cffe0be1c875cd090f82028dfda0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F115350_3ef4cffe0be1c875cd090f82028dfda0.jpg&h=b2f276e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用淨色圖當hand機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次試下更蠢D搵部Mac機放張藍色圖話藍畫面啦<br />\n或者An機放張白蘋果圖<br />\n<br />\n樓主你雖然近年叻左<br />\n開好多新聞post攝落出post紀錄度扮唔係打手<br />\n但你D打手post都一如以往常用假新聞扮到真咁<br />\n換湯不換藥<br />\n<br />\n有時間做呢D野不如自己爭氣D搵多D錢啦</blockquote><br />\n笑下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d29d9e52a1483d2f60193243674c3dd9deec939","tid":146291,"uid":62004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"任記出機通常都係市面上早就成熟既技術<br />\n今次真係比想像中多問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2ababbdc7cf4aca2ace47106f30461d108d44f","tid":146291,"uid":42675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:21:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cb-srOfRqNc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCb-srOfRqNc&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=65650b3f\